{
  "texts": [
    "For such σ, the field K[σ] is also not sub-p-adic.",
    "□ Theorem 5.2.",
    "Let K be a finitely generated field over Q and e a positive integer.",
    "Then, for almost all σ ∈ G e K, any finite extension of K[σ] is Kummerfaithful.",
    "If e ≥ 2, then the proposition follows from Corollary 4.3."
  ]
}